// Host Config for vm/arch-data — VM smoke-test host for the multi data-pools
// ownership check (pool-owners, ADR 0031).
//
// Merged on top of `.os/hosts/core/config.jsonc`. Declares one user
// (vm-data — a secrets-free user, so secrets_load is a no-op) so the
// installer's pool-owners step has a Primary User to own the /data pools;
// ships no system programs to keep the install light and focused on
// data-pool ownership.

{
  "users": ["vm-data"],
  "system_programs": []
}
